Description: Yet Another Kubernetes Distribution (program)
 This package contains the yakd utility, used to manage the yakd debian-based
 Kubernetes distribution.  Facilities include building images, installing
 images, facilitating system installation, and upgrading running systems.
 See the README at github.com/mtaylor91/yakd.git for more information.
